Package src.camp_management

Class CampList

java.lang.Object
src.camp_management.CampList
public class CampList extends Object
The CampList class represents a list of camps and provides methods for managing and interacting with the camp data. It includes functionality for initializing, adding, deleting, sorting, and retrieving information about camps.

This class utilizes the CampInfo class to represent individual camps and the CampSorter class for sorting the camps. The camp list can be manipulated, and various details about camps can be accessed through the provided methods.
